# Hotfix Post-Mortems Directory

This directory contains post-mortem documentation for hotfix releases.

## Naming Convention

Each post-mortem file must be named after the hotfix tag:
- `v4.1.2-hotfix.1.md`
- `v4.1.3-hotfix.1.md`

## Template

See [HOTFIX_OVERRIDE.md](../HOTFIX_OVERRIDE.md) for the required template.

## Enforcement

The `hotfix-postmortem-enforcer.yml` workflow runs daily to check for missing post-mortems.
